name: TUG BOATS
description:
This is a print of a photograph taken of tug boats on the docks of Portsmouth, New Hampshire. 

The photograph is printed at a professional lab on *EXTREMELY* archival Hahnemuhle fine art pearl paper using archival pigment inks. This combination of ink and paper last 200+ years. They can also be adopted other sizes. Please contact me if you would like to custom order a different size. Prices increase as editions begin to sell out.

***This is part of an edition of 15 per size. The price increases as the editions run out.***

Each print comes with a personal, handwritten thank you card from me, the photographer.
